{"aid": "http://arxiv.org/abs/2504.15014v1", "title": "Computations of Spin-Sp(4), Spin-SU(8), and Spin-Spin(16) bordism groups
  in dimensions up to 7", "summary": "We investigate the structure of Spin-$G$ bordism groups, focusing on the
interplay between Spin and additional twisting symmetries such as $Sp(4)$,
$SU(8)$ and $Spin(16)$. Using techniques from spectral sequences, obstruction
theory, and cohomology operations, we compute explicit generators for the
